# Employee Management System

## 📌 Project Description
This is a simple Employee Management System built using ASP.NET Core MVC and Entity Framework Core using Code First approach.

The system allows managing employees and departments with full CRUD operations, search functionality, and validation.

---

## 🚀 Features

### Employee Module:
- Add new employee
- Edit employee information
- Delete employee
- View employee details
- Search employees by name or department
- Display employee active status

### Department Module:
- Add new department
- Edit department
- Delete department (with validation if it contains employees)
- View department details

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used
- ASP.NET Core MVC
- Entity Framework Core (Code First)
- SQL Server
- Repository Pattern
- Service Layer Pattern
- Bootstrap 5
- LINQ

